    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1696200/extras/30def7c58ddcd36ad82f22d0096c783e.poster.avif?t=1728027417\" width=534 height=704 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1696200/extras/30def7c58ddcd36ad82f22d0096c783e.webm?t=1728027417\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1696200/extras/30def7c58ddcd36ad82f22d0096c783e.mp4?t=1728027417\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>地狱不会自己消失......</strong><br><br><strong>你必须采取行动!</strong><br><br>进入地狱爆破手，这群臭名昭著的雇佣兵决心要结束这场长期战争。玩街机模式5个级别不断发射断子弹，或者在故事模式中跟随温特和夏天的故事，完成36个级别中结束战争!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1696200/extras/9e46ce619f247e43dffb0b55c902cb82.poster.avif?t=1728027417\" width=532 height=212 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1696200/extras/9e46ce619f247e43dffb0b55c902cb82.webm?t=1728027417\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1696200/extras/9e46ce619f247e43dffb0b55c902cb82.mp4?t=1728027417\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>街机模式分为5个级别的子弹地狱!<br></li><li>故事模式分为36个级别的小规模射击旅程! 非常适合休闲地玩游戏。<br></li><li>生动的小说式故事模式! 享受地狱爆破手的旅程和他们为恢复和平所做的斗争!<br></li><li>玩扮演两个不同的角色。温特用她迅速而锋利的蔚蓝之剑，或夏天用他凶猛的深红之斧!<br></li><li>分数攻击模式测试你的射击技巧! 你能胜任成为最佳射手的任务吗？<br></li><li>5种难度模式适合于各种水平的玩家！简单模式适合新手，普通模式适合有经验的玩家，困难模式适合专家，一般模式适合挑战者，记者模式适合记者！<br></li><li>在动态排列模式中挑战自己！你能挑战动态难度吗？<br></li><li>享受Vibetronic令人血脉喷张的原声音乐和新编的配乐!<br></li><li>屏幕缩放选项（包括TATE/垂直模式）和重播!</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1696200/extras/9bb7d9b30e770c88a34da7918b4f4e33.poster.avif?t=1728027417\" width=540 height=616 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1696200/extras/9bb7d9b30e770c88a34da7918b4f4e33.webm?t=1728027417\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1696200/extras/9bb7d9b30e770c88a34da7918b4f4e33.mp4?t=1728027417\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
